<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-42-0376 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper briefly summarizes all aspects of drilling and completing ageothermal well. It discusses predrill planning and considerations including:types of fluid in the reservoir, pressure and temperature of the reservoir,production rate, required surface pressure, type of production zone,anticipated lithology, and any known or anticipated problems. It alsodiscusses and compares the differences between drilling and completinga geothermal well and an oil and gas well.</TEXT></DOC>